.SH "API REFERENCE"

This command uses the \fBcompute/beta\fR API. The full documentation for this
API can be found at:
https://developers.google.com/compute/docs/reference/latest/



.SH "EXAMPLES"

To add an IAM policy binding for the role of 'roles/compute.securityAdmin' for
the user 'test\-user@gmail.com' with instance 'my\-instance' and zone 'ZONE',
run:

.RS 2m
$ gcloud beta compute instances add\-iam\-policy\-binding my\-instance \e
    \-\-zone='ZONE' \-\-member='user:test\-user@gmail.com' \e
    \-\-role='roles/compute.securityAdmin'
.RE

See https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/managing\-policies for details of policy
role and member types.



